        "subject": "LU-5768 tests: Disable replay-single 52 and 73b",
        "message": "LU-5768 tests: Disable replay-single 52 and 73b\n\nBoth replay-single 52 and 73b (with current b2_5 code) may drop\nenqueue reqeusts for MGS locks instead of lock replays.  This causes a\nhigh rate of failures, preventing innocent patches from landing.\n\nChange-Id: Ifdfd121e261727e28ebf11518e4198ebb694aeea\nSigned-off-by: Li Wei <wei.g.li@intel.com>\n"
      },
